  <span id="freeText304929169774113009" style="display:none"> There's a lovely mix of witty and hilarious dialogue and banter. An enjoyable read, a great revisit to some favorite characters, but a little stale in parts. I love Paul, but I wish they had a better cover designer. These books are excellent but sadly overlooked. </span>
